data.description: Beautiful two story, 4 bedroom, 3 and a half bath, 2 car garage. When you enter the high ceilings will welcome you to the formal dining, office/study and the wrought iron stairway that lead you upstairs to three bedrooms, two bathrooms, and game room. The kitchen boosts an island open to the living room for family gatherings. Breakfast area with bar/desk area for multiple uses. The den/family room is spacious with fireplace, windows with shutters that offer lots of natural light.  The primary bedroom with the en-suite primary bath has soaking tub, standing shower and two large closets.   The backyard offers a patio for cooking and hanging out with friends and family.   Property is located on a quiet cul-de-sac adjacent to greenspace and close to walking, jogging, and bike trails. Schedule your private showing today!!  Motivated Seller!!
